thread.title: Janeane Lee
thread.title_full: Springfield Camping reviewed by Janeane Lee

author: Janeane Lee
title: Janeane Lee
text:
Ordered a Vango awning and accessories and it was delivered to me in Australia in 4 days. It was very well packaged and very pleased with the service from Adrian who followed up on all my questions and concerns.
The awning looks fantastic and very pleased with the quality cannot wait to try it out later this week.
